@Node "Groups" "phonebill.guide/Groups"
@Next "Presets"
@Prev "Settings"
@Toc "Menus"

Groups
======

   Note: this menu is only available if groups have been defined. See
@{"Group settings panel" Link "Group settings panel"}.

   If the @{b}Default@{ub} item is checked, all hosts will be taken into account
when generating reports. However, if @{b}Default@{ub} is not checked, only hosts
that are member of the checked groups will appear in the reports.


@EndNode

@Node "Presets" "phonebill.guide/Presets"
@Prev "Groups"
@Toc "Menus"

Presets
=======

   Note: this menu is only available if presets have been defined. See
@{"Report presets panel" Link "Report presets panel"}.

   Using this menu you can use the settings of the selected preset.


@EndNode

